 <h2>2. Lunch </h2>
 <ul>
   <li>Main course: Build-your-Own Sandwich</li>
   <ol>
     <li>start with two slices of Sourdough Bread</li>
     <li>Add a layer of Turkey slices </li>
     <li>Place Swiss Cheese on top</li>
     <li>Finish with lettuce and tomato </li>
   </ol>
   <li>Side: Potato chips</li>
   <li>Beverage: Iced tea</li>
 </ul>
 <h2>3. Dinner</h2>
 <ul>
   <li>Appetizer: Garlic bread </li>
