   <ol>
     <li>First,plate the cooked spaghetti </li>
     <li>Next,ladle the bolognese sauce over the pasta</li>
     <li>Finally,Sprinkle with grated parmesan cheese</li>
   </ol>
   <li>Dessert : Tiramisu </li>
 </ul>
